is case).\n     *\n     * @return A list of all path param templates that were defined in the request\n     * @see #getUndefinedPathParamPlaceholders()\n     */\n    List<String> getPathParamPlaceholders();\n}"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1780939264041}}
